frame_0.jpg.description: The image shows a busy urban intersection with multiple vehicles, pedestrians, and street signs. Traffic lights are visible, with a prominent red light for the car's lane. Pedestrians are crossing the street from the left. Vehicles are queued up ahead, waiting for the light to change. A yellow taxi is parked to the left, and signs indicate a mandatory turn.
frame_0.jpg.do: Stop at the red light, wait for pedestrians to clear the crosswalk, prepare to make the required turn when the light turns green.
frame_0.jpg.dont: Proceed through the red light, obstruct the pedestrian crosswalk, make abrupt lane changes.

frame_1.jpg.description: The image shows an urban intersection with multiple cars and pedestrians. A white car is directly ahead, waiting to cross the intersection. A pedestrian in a red hoodie is crossing the street. There are several visible signs including a no left turn sign and a pedestrian crosswalk signal.
frame_1.jpg.do: Stop and yield to the pedestrian crossing the street. Wait for the white car in front to proceed before moving.
frame_1.jpg.dont: Proceed through the intersection until it is clear of pedestrians and vehicles.

frame_2.jpg.description: The image shows a busy urban street intersection with a no right turn sign, cars waiting at a red light, and a pedestrian crosswalk with people crossing. A couple of pedestrians are walking on the sidewalk while one person crosses the street.
frame_2.jpg.do: Stop at the red light and wait for it to turn green. Monitor pedestrian movement closely, ensuring all pedestrians have cleared the crosswalk before proceeding.
frame_2.jpg.dont: Make a right turn or move forward while the light is red and pedestrians are crossing.

frame_3.jpg.description: The image shows a busy urban intersection with vehicles and pedestrians. A car ahead is signaling a right turn. Several pedestrians are walking in the crosswalk. Traffic lights and street signs are visible, including a no-left-turn sign.
frame_3.jpg.do: Wait until pedestrian crosswalk is clear before proceeding. Prepare to follow the vehicle ahead for a right turn.
frame_3.jpg.dont: Enter the intersection while pedestrians are crossing. Make a left turn due to posted signage.

frame_4.jpg.description: The image shows a city intersection with a red traffic light. There is a white vehicle stopped in front with pedestrians crossing the street. Buildings and traffic signs are visible including 'No Entry' and 'No Left Turn'.
frame_4.jpg.do: Stay stopped behind the vehicle ahead as the light is red and ensure that pedestrians have cleared the crossing before proceeding.
frame_4.jpg.dont: Proceed through the intersection on red light or attempt to make a left turn where prohibited.

frame_5.jpg.description: The image shows an intersection with a white car in front of the self-driving car, waiting at a red traffic light. There is a pedestrian crossing the road from left to right and several traffic signs indicating no left turn and turn right only. The road is marked with an arrow directing right turns.
frame_5.jpg.do: Wait for the traffic light to turn green and proceed to turn right.
frame_5.jpg.dont: Make any left turn or proceed through the red light.

frame_6.jpg.description: The image shows an intersection with a white car ahead stopped at a red traffic light. There is a pedestrian crossing the street with a countdown signal showing 7 seconds remaining. Signs indicate no left turn and no entry into Market Street for all vehicles except MUNI buses.
frame_6.jpg.do: Stop and wait for the red light to turn green. Remain stationary until the pedestrian has completely crossed the street.
frame_6.jpg.dont: Proceed into the intersection or attempt a left turn into Market Street.

frame_7.jpg.description: The image shows an urban intersection with a white car making a right turn. The traffic light is red, and there are multiple traffic signs including a no left turn sign and a no entry sign for certain vehicles. Pedestrians are visible on the sidewalk.
frame_7.jpg.do: Stop and wait for the green light before proceeding. Follow the traffic signs and prepare to go straight as right turns are not allowed.
frame_7.jpg.dont: Proceed through the red light. Make a right or left turn against traffic signals and signs.

frame_8.jpg.description: The image shows a city intersection with a red traffic light, a pedestrian crossing countdown showing 5 seconds, a 'No Left Turn' sign, and a white car making a left turn. The surrounding environment includes buildings and some greenery.
frame_8.jpg.do: Stop at the intersection and wait for the traffic light to turn green before proceeding.
frame_8.jpg.dont: Make a left turn into the street with a 'No Left Turn' sign.

frame_9.jpg.description: The image shows an intersection with traffic lights. The traffic light is red, and there is a sign indicating no left turn. Pedestrians are crossing from the left side of the road. A countdown pedestrian signal displays 4 seconds.
frame_9.jpg.do: Stop at the intersection and wait for the red light to change to green.
frame_9.jpg.dont: Proceed through the intersection or make a left turn.

frame_10.jpg.description: The image shows an urban intersection with a red traffic light. There is a pedestrian crosswalk marked with white patterns. A pedestrian in a wheelchair is waiting near the crossing area. Several buildings surround the intersection, and a 'No Left Turn' sign is visible.
frame_10.jpg.do: Stop at the red light and wait until the signal turns green. Monitor the pedestrian in a wheelchair for potential crossing.
frame_10.jpg.dont: Proceed through the intersection during the red light phase.

frame_11.jpg.description: The image shows an urban street intersection with a red traffic light and a pedestrian in a wheelchair crossing the street. There is a countdown pedestrian signal showing two seconds remaining. Nearby are several pedestrians on the sidewalk, and there are signs indicating no entry for certain vehicles.
frame_11.jpg.do: Come to a complete stop and wait for the traffic light to turn green and the pedestrian to clear the crosswalk.
frame_11.jpg.dont: Proceed through the intersection while the light is red and pedestrians are crossing.

frame_12.jpg.description: The image shows a city intersection with traffic lights. There is a person on a motorized wheelchair crossing the street directly in front of the camera. The traffic light is red for vehicles in the direction of the camera. A 'No Left Turn' sign is visible.
frame_12.jpg.do: Stop and wait for the red light to turn green. Allow the person crossing in the wheelchair to cross safely.
frame_12.jpg.dont: Proceed through the red light or make a left turn where prohibited.

frame_13.jpg.description: The image shows a city intersection with traffic lights. The light is red, and pedestrians are visible on the crosswalk. There is a 'No Left Turn' sign except for public transport. Sidewalks and buildings are around the intersection.
frame_13.jpg.do: Stop at the red light and wait for it to turn green before proceeding.
frame_13.jpg.dont: Make a left turn into the restricted street unless the vehicle is public transport.

frame_16.jpg.do: Stop at the red light and yield to pedestrians crossing the road.
frame_16.jpg.dont: Proceed through the intersection or make a left turn.

frame_17.jpg.description: The image depicts an intersection in an urban environment with a pedestrian crossing from left to right in front of the car. The traffic light is red, and there are signs prohibiting turns into the street except for buses. Buildings and trees are visible in the background.
frame_17.jpg.do: Stop at the red light and wait for it to turn green. Monitor the pedestrian crossing in front of the vehicle.

frame_18.jpg.description: The image shows an urban intersection with traffic lights. The light is red, and pedestrians are crossing the street. There is a 'no left turn' sign visible.

frame_19.jpg.dont: Proceed through the intersection or attempt a left turn.

frame_71.jpg.description: The image shows a city street on a rainy day with parked cars on both sides. There are two large trucks ahead partially blocking the lanes. frame_71.jpg.do: Prepare to stop as the light is red; maintain a safe distance from the trucks; monitor the pedestrian's movement closely; be cautious of the wet road conditions.
frame_71.jpg.dont: Proceed at normal speed through the intersection; attempt to overtake the trucks; ignore the pedestrian or the red light.

frame_72.jpg.description: The image shows an urban street scene on a wet day with parked cars lining both sides of the street. There are visible traffic light signals with a red light. A few vehicles are stopped at the light, and the road is slick with water.
frame_72.jpg.do: Come to a complete stop before the traffic lights. Maintain awareness of pedestrians and other vehicles. Prepare to proceed once the lights turn green.
frame_72.jpg.dont: Proceed through the red light. Speed up on the wet and slick road. Switch lanes unnecessarily.

frame_73.jpg.description: The image shows a wet urban street on a rainy day with parked cars on the left and moving vehicles on the right. A pedestrian with an umbrella is crossing the road in front of a large white truck, near a traffic light showing red.
frame_73.jpg.do: Slow down and be prepared to stop for the pedestrian crossing the road; maintain a safe following distance from vehicles ahead.
frame_73.jpg.dont: Speed up or change lanes abruptly.

frame_74.jpg.description: The image depicts a city street on a rainy day with wet pavement. Several vehicles, including two large trucks and parked cars, are visible. Pedestrians with umbrellas are on the sidewalk. The street goes uphill, and traffic lights are present.
frame_74.jpg.do: Proceed with caution, maintain a safe distance from vehicles, monitor pedestrian activity, and be prepared to stop due to wet road conditions.
frame_74.jpg.dont: Rush through the intersection, ignore pedestrians crossing, drive too closely to the trucks.

frame_75.jpg.description: The image shows a wet urban street with multiple vehicles, including parked cars on the left and two large trucks on the right. There are pedestrians crossing the street ahead, and a traffic signal is visible with a red light, indicating that the self-driving car should stop. Buildings line both sides of the street, and it's raining lightly, creating a slick road surface.
frame_75.jpg.do: Stop at the intersection. Wait for pedestrians to cross and for the traffic light to turn green before proceeding cautiously on the wet road.
frame_75.jpg.dont: Proceed through the red light or into the intersection before pedestrians have cleared the crossing.

frame_76.jpg.description: The image shows an urban street with wet pavement on a rainy day. Vehicles are parked on both sides of the street. A white SUV is crossing an intersection ahead, and a large truck is occupying the right lane. Traffic lights are visible, with some construction cones and signs indicating ongoing roadwork.
frame_76.jpg.do: Proceed with caution, yield to crossing vehicles, and be prepared to stop for pedestrian or traffic lights.
frame_76.jpg.dont: Speed, change lanes abruptly, or ignore traffic light signals.

frame_77.jpg.description: The image shows a wet street in an urban environment. There is a white SUV crossing an intersection while the traffic light is red. A large white truck is stopped at the intersection, and there are pedestrians crossing the street. Buildings line both sides of the street, and additional vehicles are visible parked and driving. It's raining, indicated by wet pavement and visible water droplets.
frame_77.jpg.do: Stop at the intersection, monitor pedestrian crossing, and wait for the light to turn green before proceeding.
frame_77.jpg.dont: Proceed through the red light or ignore pedestrians crossing.

frame_78.jpg.description: The image shows a wet urban street with several vehicles and pedestrians. A large truck is stopped ahead, and a few cars are waiting at an intersection. Pedestrians are crossing the street, some with umbrellas. Traffic lights are red, and the road is shiny from recent rain.
frame_78.jpg.do: Maintain a safe distance from the truck and prepare to stop. Monitor pedestrian crossings and wait until the traffic light turns green.
frame_78.jpg.dont: Proceed through the red light or make any abrupt maneuvers that could endanger pedestrians or other vehicles.

frame_79.jpg.description: A rainy urban street intersection with a red traffic light. Pedestrians holding umbrellas cross from left to right. A large truck is stationary in the right lane, while a few vehicles are parked along the side of the road. Traffic cones are present further ahead indicating potential roadwork or lane closure.
frame_79.jpg.do: Remain stationary while the traffic light is red. Monitor crosswalk for pedestrians. Prepare to proceed only when the light turns green and the crosswalk is clear.
frame_79.jpg.dont: Enter the intersection on red. Proceed while pedestrians are in the crosswalk. Ignore potential obstacles from roadwork ahead.

frame_80.jpg.description: The image shows a multi-lane urban road with light traffic. Vehicles are moving in both directions. A large truck is in the left lane, and several cars are visible ahead and to the right. The traffic light in the distance is green.
frame_80.jpg.do: Continue moving forward, maintain a safe distance from the vehicles ahead, adjust speed according to traffic conditions.

frame_81.jpg.description: The image shows a multi-lane city street with moderate traffic. There is a large truck on the left lane and several cars in the middle and right lanes. The traffic light in the distance is green. Buildings and trees line both sides of the street.
frame_81.jpg.do: Maintain a safe following distance and prepare to stop if the traffic light changes.
frame_81.jpg.dont: Change lanes abruptly or exceed speed limits.

frame_82.jpg.description: The image shows a multi-lane urban street with several vehicles including a large truck on the left and multiple cars ahead. Buildings line both sides of the road, and the traffic lights ahead appear to be green.
frame_82.jpg.do: Maintain lane and speed, continue moving forward while monitoring traffic lights and other vehicles.
frame_82.jpg.dont: Change lanes abruptly or speed up rapidly, especially near the truck or surrounding vehicles.

frame_83.jpg.description: The image shows a multi-lane city street with moderate traffic. There is a large truck on the left and several cars ahead and to the right. Buildings line the street on both sides, and there are traffic lights visible in the distance.
frame_83.jpg.do: Maintain a safe following distance from the vehicles ahead and prepare to slow down if traffic conditions change.
frame_83.jpg.dont: Change lanes abruptly or accelerate aggressively.

frame_84.jpg.description: A multi-lane road in an urban area with moderate traffic. A large truck is in the left lane and several cars are ahead in the middle and right lanes. Buildings and trees line the sides. A traffic signal is visible and appears to be green.
frame_84.jpg.do: Maintain a safe following distance from the vehicles ahead and continue at current speed observing the traffic signal.
frame_84.jpg.dont: Sudden lane changes, speeding, or stopping abruptly unless necessary.

frame_85.jpg.description: The image shows a multi-lane urban street with several vehicles ahead and to the sides. A large truck is in the left lane, cars are in the middle and right lanes. Traffic lights are visible ahead, and pedestrians are on the sidewalks.

frame_85.jpg.dont: Change lanes abruptly, proceed through the intersection while the light is red.

frame_86.jpg.description: The image shows a multi-lane urban street with vehicles, including a large truck on the left. Traffic lights are present, with red and yellow lights illuminated. The street is surrounded by buildings.

frame_86.jpg.dont: Proceed through the intersection until the light turns green.

frame_91.jpg.description: The image shows a busy city intersection with a red traffic light. Several vehicles, including a large truck and multiple cars, are stopped at the intersection. Buildings and trees line the streets, and pedestrians are visible on the sidewalks.

frame_91.jpg.dont: Proceed through the intersection while the light is red

frame_93.jpg.description: The image shows a busy city intersection with multiple lanes of traffic. frame_97.jpg.description: The image shows a busy urban intersection with multiple vehicles and a pedestrian crossing the street. The traffic light is red, and cars are stopped at the intersection. A large truck is visible on the left, a dark sedan in the center, and a red car on the right.

frame_109.jpg.description: The image shows a dimly lit urban street at night with several parked cars on both sides and a vehicle moving ahead. Street lights and traffic lights are visible in the distance.

frame_110.jpg.description: Nighttime street scene with parked cars on both sides and a vehicle moving ahead in the center of the lane. Streetlights and a green traffic light are visible in the distance.

frame_1940.jpg.dont: Proceed through the red light or change lanes abruptly.

frame_1941.jpg.description: The image shows a multi-lane road with vehicles stopped at a red light at an intersection. There are traffic lights visible, with the lights for the direction of travel being red. The intersection is clearly marked, and there are several vehicles waiting in adjacent lanes.
frame_1941.jpg.do: Stop and wait at the red light. Monitor surrounding vehicles for any changes in movement.
frame_1941.jpg.dont: Proceed through the intersection while the light is red. Change lanes unexpectedly.

frame_1942.jpg.description: The image shows a multi-lane intersection with traffic signals displaying green lights in the direction of travel. Several vehicles are lined up and proceeding through the intersection. There are also pedestrians on the sidewalk.
frame_1942.jpg.do: Proceed straight through the intersection while monitoring the traffic and pedestrians.
frame_1942.jpg.dont: Change lanes abruptly or stop suddenly without reason.

frame_1943.jpg.description: The image shows a traffic intersection with multiple lanes. The traffic lights are green for the lanes going straight and red for the left turn lane. There are several vehicles ahead, including a black pickup truck and a white truck. Pedestrians are present on the right side of the intersection.
frame_1943.jpg.do: Proceed straight with caution, maintaining a safe distance from the vehicle ahead.
frame_1943.jpg.dont: Turn left or enter the pedestrian crosswalk while pedestrians are crossing.

frame_1944.jpg.description: The image shows a busy intersection with multiple lanes. Traffic signals are visible, with two green lights and one red light for different lanes. Several vehicles are present, some moving straight and others preparing to turn. Trees and buildings border the roads.
frame_1944.jpg.do: Proceed straight with caution as the traffic light is green for the lane ahead. Monitor nearby vehicles' movements.
frame_1944.jpg.dont: Stop abruptly in the lane or make unplanned turns.

frame_1945.jpg.description: A busy intersection with multiple vehicles in front. The traffic light is green, allowing cars to proceed. There are cars in both the left and right lanes, with a clear path in the center lane.
frame_1945.jpg.do: Proceed straight at a moderate speed, maintaining a safe distance from the vehicle ahead.
frame_1945.jpg.dont: Change lanes abruptly or accelerate rapidly.

frame_1946.jpg.description: The image shows a busy intersection with multiple lanes of traffic. The traffic light ahead is green, and several vehicles are proceeding through the intersection. Palm trees and buildings are visible on both sides of the road.
frame_1946.jpg.do: Proceed through the intersection while maintaining the current lane and observing other vehicles for potential lane changes.
frame_1946.jpg.dont: Accelerate abruptly or change lanes without signaling.

frame_1947.jpg.description: The image shows a busy intersection with cars in multiple lanes going straight. The traffic light is green for going straight but red for turning left. There is a pedestrian crossing area visible.
frame_1947.jpg.do: Proceed straight through the intersection while monitoring for traffic and pedestrians.
frame_1947.jpg.dont: Turn left; wait for green arrow light.

frame_1948.jpg.description: The image shows a street intersection with a green traffic light ahead for the direction of travel. Several vehicles are moving forward, and a left-turn signal is red. There are multiple lanes, including a lane for left turns, and traffic is moderate. Buildings and trees are visible on both sides of the road.
frame_1948.jpg.do: Continue driving straight with caution, maintaining a safe distance from the vehicle ahead.

frame_1950.jpg.description: The image shows a multi-lane road with light traffic. Vehicles are moving in both directions. There is a clear blue sky and a few trees lining the road. Shops are visible on the right side with a visible speed limit sign of 40 mph.
frame_1950.jpg.do: Maintain speed within the speed limit and keep a safe distance from the vehicle in front. Prepare for any potential lane changes.
frame_1950.jpg.dont: Tailgate the vehicle in front or exceed the speed limit.

frame_1951.jpg.description: The image shows multiple vehicles on a multi-lane road in an urban area. There are cars traveling in both directions and a median separating the lanes. Buildings and commercial establishments are visible alongside the road, with some trees providing shade.
frame_1951.jpg.do: Maintain a safe following distance from the vehicle ahead. Monitor speed and traffic signals as approaching the intersection.
frame_1951.jpg.dont: Switch lanes erratically or exceed the posted speed limit.

frame_1952.jpg.description: A multi-lane road with light traffic, including two trucks directly ahead in adjacent lanes. There are commercial buildings on the right side and a clear sky. Traffic signs and lights are visible ahead.
frame_1952.jpg.do: Maintain a safe following distance, monitor the speed of the vehicles ahead, and stay in the current lane.
frame_1952.jpg.dont: Change lanes without checking for blind spots or traffic signals, exceed the speed limit posted on the road.

frame_1953.jpg.description: The image shows a multi-lane road with clear markings and vehicles ahead. Trees and shops line the sides. The speed limit is 40. Traffic appears moderate.
frame_1953.jpg.do: Maintain current speed and stay in lane.
frame_1953.jpg.dont: Execute lane changes or increase speed.

frame_1954.jpg.description: A pedestrian crossing a multi-lane city street at a marked crosswalk with other vehicles present. Buildings and shops line both sides of the street.
frame_1954.jpg.do: Stop and wait for the pedestrian to fully cross the street before proceeding.
frame_1954.jpg.dont: Proceed or inch forward while the pedestrian is in the crosswalk.

frame_1955.jpg.description: The image shows an urban intersection with a pedestrian in the crosswalk. There are traffic lights and parked cars along the street. The pedestrian is crossing from left to right.
frame_1955.jpg.do: Stop and yield to the pedestrian crossing the road. Remain stationary until the crosswalk is clear of pedestrians.
frame_1955.jpg.dont: Proceed through the intersection while the pedestrian is in the crosswalk.

frame_1956.jpg.description: The image shows a city intersection with a pedestrian crossing from right to left on a crosswalk. There are vehicles on the road, and buildings line both sides of the street. Traffic lights are visible, indicating pedestrian crossings.
frame_1956.jpg.do: Stop and yield to the pedestrian on the crosswalk.
frame_1956.jpg.dont: Proceed through the intersection while the pedestrian is crossing.

frame_1957.jpg.description: The image shows an intersection with crosswalks and pedestrians. There are vehicles stopped at the light, shops on both sides of the street, and a pedestrian crossing the street.
frame_1957.jpg.do: Stop and wait for the pedestrian to clear the crosswalk.
frame_1957.jpg.dont: Proceed or make any turns while the pedestrian is crossing.

frame_1958.jpg.description: The image shows an urban intersection with crosswalks, buildings on either side, and a green traffic light. Cars are visible on the road, and pedestrians are on the sidewalk.
frame_1958.jpg.do: Proceed forward with caution, maintaining awareness of pedestrians and other vehicles.
frame_1958.jpg.dont: Stopping in the crosswalk or proceeding into the intersection if the light changes.

frame_1959.jpg.description: The image shows an urban street intersection with a green traffic light and a pedestrian signal indicating it's safe to walk. There are several cars on the road, some approaching the intersection. Buildings with shops line both sides of the street. Pedestrians are visible on the sidewalks.
frame_1959.jpg.do: Proceed through the intersection while monitoring for pedestrians and other vehicles.
frame_1959.jpg.dont: Stop or hesitate unnecessarily at the green light.

frame_1960.jpg.description: The image shows a urban street scene at an intersection with a green traffic light. Several cars are visible on the road, and pedestrians are present on the sidewalk. Buildings line both sides of the street.
frame_1960.jpg.do: Proceed with caution through the intersection, observing the green traffic light. Monitor the pedestrians on the sidewalk.
frame_1960.jpg.dont: Stop or slow down abruptly unless necessary, ignore pedestrian activity near the curb.

frame_1961.jpg.description: Urban street with multiple lanes, vehicles moving in both directions, pedestrians on sidewalks, and visible businesses. A crosswalk is ahead, and some pedestrians appear close to it.
frame_1961.jpg.do: Slow down and prepare to stop if pedestrians enter the crosswalk.
frame_1961.jpg.dont: Proceed quickly through the crosswalk area.

frame_1962.jpg.description: The image shows a slightly busy urban street with two lanes, cars parked along both sides, a white car approaching head-on in the left lane, pedestrians on the right sidewalk, and various shopfronts and buildings on both sides.
frame_1962.jpg.do: Ensure the car stays in its lane, maintain a safe speed, and monitor the white car approaching in the opposite direction.
frame_1962.jpg.dont: Move into oncoming lane or approach too close to parked vehicles. Steer onto the sidewalk.

frame_1963.jpg.description: The image shows a two-lane street in a city with cars parked along both sides. There are trees, buildings, and a few pedestrians near a bus stop on the right side of the road. The weather appears clear and the road is unobstructed.
frame_1963.jpg.do: Proceed with caution along the road, maintaining a safe distance from parked cars and monitoring for any pedestrians entering the roadway.
frame_1963.jpg.dont: Suddenly stop or swerve into other lanes, especially where pedestrians are present near the sidewalk.

frame_1964.jpg.description: A clear urban street with parked cars on both sides. There are pedestrians on the right sidewalk, and the road appears empty with no other vehicles in motion.
frame_1964.jpg.do: Proceed straight while maintaining a safe speed and be prepared to stop for any sudden pedestrian movement.
frame_1964.jpg.dont: Enter the sidewalk area or swerve into parked vehicles.

frame_1965.jpg.description: The image shows a city street with parked cars on both sides, a wide road clear of traffic, some pedestrians on the sidewalk, trees lining the street, and residential buildings with businesses on the ground floor.
frame_1965.jpg.do: Proceed straight with caution, maintaining the speed limit and scanning for any pedestrians or sudden openings from the parked cars.
frame_1965.jpg.dont: Stop abruptly without reason. Make sudden lane changes.

frame_1966.jpg.description: The image shows a clear urban street lined with parked cars on both sides. There are trees and buildings along the sidewalk. A few pedestrians are visible on the sidewalk, and the street appears to be well-lit with no immediate obstacles in the road. The traffic light in the distance is red.
frame_1966.jpg.do: Proceed forward with caution, maintaining a safe speed and prepare to stop at the red light ahead.
frame_1966.jpg.dont: Accelerate towards the intersection or move into parked car lanes.

frame_1967.jpg.description: A city street with parked cars on both sides and a pedestrian crossing in the distance. Buildings line the street, and there is light traffic.
frame_1967.jpg.do: Proceed with caution and prepare to yield to the pedestrian.
frame_1967.jpg.dont: Accelerate or make sudden lane changes.

frame_1968.jpg.description: Urban street with parked cars on both sides, clear lane in the center, pedestrians on the sidewalk, and a green traffic signal ahead.
frame_1968.jpg.do: Proceed straight ahead, maintain a moderate speed, and be prepared to stop if the traffic signal changes.
frame_1968.jpg.dont: Swerve into oncoming traffic lanes or park in the middle of the street.

frame_1969.jpg.description: A city street with parked cars on both sides and a slight incline. Trees line the street, and there is visible foot traffic on the sidewalk. The road is clear with no immediate obstacles in the path.
frame_1969.jpg.do: Maintain current speed, stay in lane, prepare to stop if pedestrians approach crosswalks.
frame_1969.jpg.dont: Veer into parking lanes, accelerate rapidly.

frame_1970.jpg.description: A city street lined with parked cars on both sides, clear road ahead with a slight uphill slope, and a traffic signal in the distance.
frame_1970.jpg.do: Proceed with caution, maintain current speed, and prepare to stop if the traffic signal changes.

frame_1971.jpg.description: The image shows a city street with parked cars on both sides and a pedestrian crossing the street from left to right. There is a traffic light visible slightly ahead and to the right which appears to be red. Buildings line both sides of the street, and the road is clear of any immediate obstacles.
frame_1971.jpg.do: Maintain a stop position as the traffic light ahead is red and a pedestrian is crossing the road.
frame_1971.jpg.dont: Proceed forward through the intersection while the traffic light is red and pedestrians are crossing.

frame_1972.jpg.description: The image shows a two-way street lined with parked cars on both sides. There are buildings with shops and apartments along the street. Pedestrians are visible on the sidewalk, and traffic signals and crosswalks are present.
frame_1972.jpg.do: Proceed forward at a regulated speed and monitor for pedestrians crossing at the crosswalks. Be prepared to stop if the traffic signal ahead turns red or pedestrians appear on the crosswalk.
frame_1972.jpg.dont: Accelerate rapidly or make sudden stops without cause.

frame_1973.jpg.description: A city street with buildings on both sides, cars parked along the curb, a pedestrian crossing the street in the crosswalk from left to right, and a traffic light showing red for the car's direction.
frame_1973.jpg.do: Stop at the crosswalk, respect the red traffic light, wait for the pedestrian to cross and light to turn green.
frame_1973.jpg.dont: Proceed through the red light or cross the crosswalk while the pedestrian is crossing.

frame_1974.jpg.description: The image shows a city street with multiple lanes. There is a tow truck parked on the right side of the road in the bike lane, and several cars are moving ahead in the left lane. A green traffic light is visible in the distance, allowing traffic to proceed.
frame_1974.jpg.do: Proceed in the left lane while maintaining a safe distance from other vehicles.
frame_1974.jpg.dont: Stop suddenly or switch to the blocked bike lane.

frame_1975.jpg.description: Urban street with multiple lanes, tow truck in the right lane, vehicles moving in the middle lane, and pedestrians on the sidewalk. Green traffic light ahead.
frame_1975.jpg.do: Proceed with caution, maintain speed, monitor tow truck and pedestrian movement.
frame_1975.jpg.dont: Change lanes into the bus lane on the right.

frame_1976.jpg.description: Urban street scene with multiple lanes of traffic, including parked vehicles and moving cars. The traffic light at the intersection ahead is green. Pedestrians are on the sidewalks, and the street is flanked by buildings.
frame_1976.jpg.do: Proceed through the intersection while monitoring the green light and checking for pedestrians at the crosswalk.
frame_1976.jpg.dont: Stop unnecessarily when the traffic light is green and no obstacles are detected in the path.

frame_1977.jpg.description: The image shows an urban street with moderate traffic. The road has two visible lanes in the direction of the car. A green traffic light is ahead. There are multiple vehicles on both the left and right lanes, including a tow truck in the right lane and a delivery van in the left lane. The environment includes buildings, a bus stop, and street signs.
frame_1977.jpg.do: Continue driving straight, maintain a safe distance from the vehicles ahead, and be prepared to stop if the light changes.
frame_1977.jpg.dont: Stop abruptly or change lanes without signaling.

frame_1978.jpg.description: The image shows a city street scene with a tow truck in the right lane and a bus stop marked on the asphalt. The left lane has a larger vehicle and the traffic light ahead is green. There are buildings and some trees lining the street.
frame_1978.jpg.do: Proceed straight and maintain awareness of the tow truck and other vehicles. Continue forward as the traffic light is green.
frame_1978.jpg.dont: Enter the bus stop lane or make a left turn where restricted.

frame_1979.jpg.description: The image depicts an urban street with multiple lanes. There is a green traffic light visible, allowing traffic to proceed. A white truck is parked on the side of the road and a UPS-like delivery van is ahead. A tow truck is also present in the right lane. Tall buildings and construction sites are visible on the left side of the street.
frame_1979.jpg.do: Proceed straight with caution while maintaining a safe distance from the vehicles ahead.
frame_1979.jpg.dont: Turn right at the next intersection.

frame_1980.jpg.description: The image shows a city street with high-rise buildings on both sides. The traffic light is green, allowing the self-driving car to proceed. There is a truck parked in the right lane marked for buses, and another vehicle ahead in the same lane as the self-driving car. Pedestrians are seen on the sidewalk.
frame_1980.jpg.do: Proceed straight with caution and be mindful of pedestrians.
frame_1980.jpg.dont: Enter the bus lane or make any sudden lane changes.

frame_1981.jpg.description: The image shows a city street with a green traffic light ahead. There is a sign prohibiting left or U-turns. The bus lane is visible to the right, and there are vehicles parked along the street. A pedestrian is walking on the sidewalk.
frame_1981.jpg.do: Proceed straight through the green light while staying in the correct lane.

frame_1982.jpg.description: The image shows a busy city street with multiple lanes and a green traffic light. Several cars are visible, driving ahead in the right lanes, with one lane marked for buses only. Trees and buildings line both sides of the street. A pedestrian is present on the sidewalk to the right.
frame_1982.jpg.do: Maintain speed within limits and proceed with caution in the right lane.
frame_1982.jpg.dont: Enter the bus-only lane on the right side.

frame_1983.jpg.description: The image shows an urban street with multiple lanes. There are two tow trucks parked on the right lane, partially blocking it. Several vehicles are ahead, and there’s a pedestrian on the left sidewalk. The street is lined with buildings and a construction site on the left.
frame_1983.jpg.do: Change lanes to move into the left lane if clear. Proceed with caution.
frame_1983.jpg.dont: Stop abruptly in the middle of the road.

frame_1984.jpg.description: The image shows an urban street with construction on the left and office buildings on both sides. There are two tow trucks parked on the right side of the street, partially blocking the lane. In the distance, a large truck and multiple cars are traveling along the road.
frame_1984.jpg.do: Proceed with caution and prepare to merge slightly into the left lane to avoid parked tow trucks.

frame_1985.jpg.description: Urban street scene with several vehicles parked and oncoming traffic. Buildings line both sides of the street. A construction site is visible on the left with cones and construction workers. Traffic lights in the distance, center-left lane merges into right.
frame_1985.jpg.do: Monitor pedestrians and construction workers, maintain a safe speed, prepare to merge into the right lane if necessary.
frame_1985.jpg.dont: Enter construction zone or pass vehicles too closely.

frame_1986.jpg.description: Urban street with construction on the left, multiple parked trucks on the right, and a clear lane in the center. There's a pedestrian walking on the left side, and a large truck ahead driving in the same lane.
frame_1986.jpg.do: Maintain safe distance from the truck ahead and continue driving in the lane, be prepared to slow down if the pedestrian gets closer to the road.
frame_1986.jpg.dont: Merge into the lanes with parked trucks or change lanes suddenly.

frame_1987.jpg.description: The image shows an urban street with lanes clearly marked. There are several vehicles on the road, including a large truck and other cars in the lane. There's construction on the left with a worker present, and a parked truck on the right side. The light traffic indicates a non-congested area. Trees and buildings are visible along the street.
frame_1987.jpg.do: Maintain current speed, stay in the designated lane, and be prepared to stop if any vehicles ahead slow down or if any pedestrians enter the street.
frame_1987.jpg.dont: Change lanes unexpectedly or accelerate quickly near the construction zone.

frame_1988.jpg.description: The image shows an urban street with moderate traffic. Ahead, there are several vehicles, including a car in the lane and a truck on the side. A construction site is visible on the left with a worker present. The right lane is marked as a bus lane.
frame_1988.jpg.do: Maintain a safe distance from the car ahead, stay in lane, prepare to stop if necessary.
frame_1988.jpg.dont: Do not enter the bus-only lane.

frame_1989.jpg.description: The image shows a city street with construction on the left, a bus lane on the right, and several cars ahead, including a truck. A construction worker is visible on the left side near the construction area.
frame_1989.jpg.do: Continue driving straight in the current lane, maintaining a safe distance from the vehicle ahead. Monitor for pedestrians and construction activities.
frame_1989.jpg.dont: Switch to the bus lane or speed up unnecessarily.

frame_1990.jpg.description: The image shows an urban street with multiple lanes. Cars are visible ahead, and there is a construction site on the left with a worker in high-visibility clothing. A pedestrian is on the right sidewalk. The road indicates a 'Bus Only' lane on the right with a clear path forward.
frame_1990.jpg.do: Proceed with caution in the left lane, monitor pedestrian on the sidewalk and worker near construction site, maintain safe distance from the vehicles ahead.
frame_1990.jpg.dont: Enter the 'Bus Only' lane on the right.

frame_1991.jpg.description: The image shows an urban street with multiple cars ahead. There is ongoing construction on the left side with a crane visible. Trees line the right side of the street. A large truck and another vehicle are visible ahead. The road is clear, and there is a pedestrian visible on the right sidewalk.
frame_1991.jpg.do: Maintain a safe following distance behind the vehicle ahead, keep an eye on pedestrians and construction zones, and proceed when safe.
frame_1991.jpg.dont: Suddenly change lanes into the construction zone or accelerate abruptly.

frame_1992.jpg.description: Urban street with multiple lanes, construction on the left, vehicles ahead in lane, trees and pedestrians on the right sidewalk, and a traffic light in the distance that is green.
frame_1992.jpg.do: Continue moving forward while maintaining a safe distance from the vehicles ahead, and prepare to stop if the traffic light changes.
frame_1992.jpg.dont: Stop abruptly or change lanes unnecessarily.

frame_1993.jpg.description: The image depicts a city street with several lanes, bordered by tall buildings and trees on both sides. There is moderate traffic with a truck and a few cars ahead. Sidewalks are visible with pedestrians walking.
frame_1993.jpg.do: Maintain current speed, keep safe distance from the vehicle ahead, be prepared to stop if the traffic light changes.
frame_1993.jpg.dont: Make abrupt lane changes, exceed speed limits, ignore pedestrians on the sidewalk.

frame_1994.jpg.description: The image shows a night-time urban street scene with a car stopped ahead. To the left, a public bus is in its own lane with people walking nearby. The right side has a sidewalk, two pedestrians, and a row of lit-up shop windows.
frame_1994.jpg.do: Maintain a safe distance and be prepared to stop if the lead car or bus decelerates.
frame_1994.jpg.dont: Proceed to change lanes into the bus lane or increase speed suddenly.

frame_1995.jpg.description: The image shows a nighttime urban street with multiple lanes. There is a stationary blue sedan and a black SUV in front of the car at a standstill. A bus is parked in a designated bus lane to the left, and pedestrians are walking on the sidewalk to the right. Streetlights are on, illuminating the area.
frame_1995.jpg.do: Maintain a safe distance from the vehicles in front and prepare to move forward when the traffic starts. Monitor pedestrians on the sidewalk and be cautious of any sudden movements.
frame_1995.jpg.dont: Proceed forward without ensuring the path is clear and safe. Ignore the presence of pedestrians and the parked bus in the adjacent lane.

frame_1996.jpg.description: The image shows a nighttime urban street scene with a bus stopped to the left and two cars in the lane ahead. There are pedestrians on the sidewalk and illuminated storefronts on the right.
frame_1996.jpg.do: Slow down and maintain a safe following distance behind the vehicle ahead. Prepare to stop if the bus re-enters traffic or if pedestrians cross.
frame_1996.jpg.dont: Change lanes abruptly or speed up.

frame_1997.jpg.description: The image shows a busy urban street at night with a row of parked vehicles including a bus on the left and a car directly ahead. There are streetlights illuminating the area, buildings with lit windows, and pedestrians on the sidewalk.
frame_1997.jpg.do: Maintain a safe distance from the vehicle in front and monitor for any pedestrian crossing or sudden traffic changes.
frame_1997.jpg.dont: Proceed at high speed or make sudden lane changes.

frame_1998.jpg.description: The image shows a nighttime urban environment with a busy street. There is a bus visible on the left lane ahead, stopped to pick up or drop off passengers. There is a line of cars behind the bus, including a blue car directly in front of the self-driving vehicle. Brightly lit storefronts and street lights illuminate the area, and pedestrians are present on the sidewalk to the right.
frame_1998.jpg.do: Maintain a safe distance from the car ahead; prepare to stop or move slowly as needed. Watch for pedestrians and sudden stops from the bus.
frame_1998.jpg.dont: Stop abruptly; attempt to overtake the bus or swerve into pedestrian areas.

frame_1999.jpg.description: The image shows a city street at night with vehicles on the road. There is a blue car directly in front of the self-driving car, positioned in a lane marked for bicycles. A bus is visible on the left lane, and pedestrians are walking along the sidewalk. Streetlights and storefronts are illuminated, adding to the visibility.
frame_1999.jpg.do: Maintain a safe distance from the blue car ahead and be prepared to stop if it decelerates. Monitor for pedestrians stepping onto the road and continue to follow traffic signals.
frame_1999.jpg.dont: Enter the bicycle lane occupied by the blue car. Speed up or make sudden lane changes without checking surroundings.

frame_2000.jpg.description: The image shows a nighttime urban street scene with a blue car directly ahead, stopped in a lane bordered by a lighted bus shelter on the right. There are pedestrians on the sidewalk and a bus traveling on the adjacent lane. The street is well-lit with streetlights, and there is visible traffic in both directions.
frame_2000.jpg.do: Maintain a safe following distance from the car in front and prepare to stop if it slows or stops. Monitor pedestrians on the sidewalk and check for any crossing the street.
frame_2000.jpg.dont: Proceed at high speeds or make abrupt lane changes.

frame_2001.jpg.description: The image shows a city street at night with multiple lanes, streetlights, and a vehicle ahead. Pedestrians are nearby on the sidewalk and public transport lanes are present.
frame_2001.jpg.do: Drive with caution, maintain a steady speed, be prepared to stop for pedestrians, follow traffic signals.
frame_2001.jpg.dont: Overtake the vehicle in front, make sudden stops or turns, enter pedestrian pathways.

frame_2002.jpg.description: The image shows a busy urban street at night with streetlights illuminating the scene. There's a car in front of the self-driving vehicle, a bus to the left, and pedestrians walking on the sidewalk. The street is lined with buildings, and there's a lit advertisement on the right. A traffic light is visible in the distance.
frame_2002.jpg.do: Maintain a safe distance from the car in front, monitor the traffic light ahead, and be alert for pedestrians near the crosswalk.
frame_2002.jpg.dont: Proceed through the intersection without confirming the traffic light status, or make sudden lane changes that could affect nearby pedestrians or vehicles.

frame_2003.jpg.description: The image shows a night-time urban street scene with a car stopped at a pedestrian crossing, waiting for a green traffic light. Pedestrians are waiting on the sidewalk, and a bus is visible in the adjacent lane. Streetlights illuminate the area, and a no right turn sign is visible.
frame_2003.jpg.do: Wait for the traffic light to turn green before proceeding. Monitor pedestrian activity and be prepared to yield if they begin crossing.
frame_2003.jpg.dont: Proceed while the traffic light is red or attempt to make a right turn where prohibited.

frame_2004.jpg.description: The image shows a busy city street at night. Several pedestrians are on the sidewalk near a crosswalk, some appearing to wait to cross. There are vehicles on the road, including a bus and a car in the lane ahead. The traffic light is green, indicating go, and there are streetlights illuminating the area. Buildings line both sides of the street.
frame_2004.jpg.do: Proceed with caution due to the presence of pedestrians near the crosswalk and maintain awareness of other vehicles.
frame_2004.jpg.dont: Rush through the intersection despite having a green light due to potential pedestrian crossing.

frame_2005.jpg.description: The image shows a street at night with buildings on both sides. There is a green traffic light visible, indicating it's safe to proceed. A bus and a car are ahead in the lane. Pedestrians are on the sidewalks, and signs indicate no left turn.
frame_2005.jpg.do: Proceed straight while monitoring traffic, stay in the current lane, be prepared to yield to any unexpected pedestrian crossings.

frame_2006.jpg.description: The image shows a busy urban street at night with a green traffic light. Vehicles, including a bus and a car, are moving along the road. There are streetlights, a pedestrian crossing, and a no right turn sign visible. The environment is well-lit with several buildings on both sides of the street.
frame_2006.jpg.do: Proceed straight through the intersection while monitoring traffic and pedestrians.

frame_2007.jpg.description: The image shows a busy urban street at night with multiple vehicles including buses and a truck moving in the same direction. There are pedestrians on the sidewalk to the right. A green traffic light is visible ahead and a traffic sign indicating no right turns.
frame_2007.jpg.do: Proceed straight with caution, maintaining a safe distance from vehicles ahead and be prepared to stop for pedestrians.

frame_2008.jpg.description: The image shows a busy city street at night. There are vehicles including cars and buses on the road, streetlights are illuminated, and people are walking on the sidewalks. A green traffic light is visible ahead and there are several buildings with lit storefronts.
frame_2008.jpg.do: Proceed with caution, follow the traffic signal, maintain a safe distance from the vehicles ahead, and monitor for pedestrians.
frame_2008.jpg.dont: Proceed through red lights, overtake in crowded conditions, ignore pedestrian crossings.

frame_2009.jpg.description: The image shows a busy city street at night. There are multiple vehicles, including buses and cars, traveling along the street. Pedestrians are crossing at a crosswalk to the right. The traffic light is green, allowing vehicles to proceed. There are street lights illuminating the scene and a no-left-turn sign is visible.
frame_2009.jpg.do: Proceed with caution through the intersection, maintain safe distance from other vehicles, and be vigilant for pedestrians crossing.
frame_2009.jpg.dont: Make a left turn at the intersection.

frame_2010.jpg.description: The image depicts a busy urban street at night, illuminated by streetlights. Several buses and vehicles are visible on the road. There is a green traffic light for cars, indicating it's safe to proceed. Pedestrians are present on the sidewalk, and there are some barriers along the side of the road.
frame_2010.jpg.do: Continue driving forward at a safe speed while monitoring for any pedestrians or vehicles that may enter the lane.
frame_2010.jpg.dont: Sudden stops or lane changes without assessing traffic conditions.

frame_2011.jpg.description: The image shows a nighttime urban street scene with multiple lanes. A green traffic light is visible above, indicating the car can proceed. A bus is stopped on the left lane, another vehicle is in motion in the right lane, and a pedestrian is seen on the sidewalk near the corner.
frame_2011.jpg.do: Proceed through the intersection while maintaining speed appropriate for an urban environment.
frame_2011.jpg.dont: Change lanes or stop suddenly unless necessary.

frame_2012.jpg.description: The image shows a nighttime urban street scene with a bus approaching a traffic stop and a pedestrian standing nearby on the sidewalk. There are illuminated streetlights, buildings, and a neon sign, and visible traffic signals showing green.
frame_2012.jpg.do: Proceed with caution, maintaining a safe distance from the vehicles ahead and be prepared to stop if signals change.
frame_2012.jpg.dont: Drive aggressively or at high speed. Ignore surrounding pedestrians or traffic signals.
